X_1
 \sigma^2=(1-{1\over24})^2\cdot {4\over 6}\cdot {1\over4}  +  {({-1\over4}-{1\over24})^2}\cdot{4\over6}\cdot{3\over4}+({1\over24})^2\cdot{2\over6} \approx 0.19618.  
\mu_S=30\mu=30/24
 \sigma^2_S=30\sigma^2\approx 5.9375.
P[S\ge 8]\approx P\Biggl[Z\ge{ 8-{30\over24}\over \sqrt{ 5.9375} }\Biggr]\approx P[Z\ge{2.7701}]\approx0.002802. 
